<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3670878>
    dc:description "FIGURES 411–422. Wings: 411: Fergusonina sp. (Fergusoninidae); 412: Odontoloxozus longicornis (Coquillett) (Neriidae); 413: Clisa australis (McAlpine) (Cypselosomatidae); 414: Formicosepsis sp. (Cypselosomatidae); 415: Pseudopomyza (Rhinopomyzella) nigrimana Hennig (Pseudopomyzidae); 416: Latheticomyia sp. (Pseudopomyzidae); 417: Nartshukia musiva Shatalkin, holotype (Strongylophthalmyiidae); 418: Strongylophthalmyia angustipennis Melander (Strongylophthalmyiidae); 419: Tanypeza longimana Fallén (Tanypezidae); 420: Neotanypeza marshalli Lonsdale (Tanypezidae); 421: Compsobata mima (Hennig) (Micropezidae); 422: Micropeza sp. (Micropezidae)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3670878/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3670825>
    dc:description "FIGURES 205–215. Cypselosoma gephyrae Hendel (Cypselosomatidae), male; 205: dorsal; 206: lateral; 207: ventrolateral; 208: head, posterior; 209: head, dorsal; 210: head, anterior. Figs 211–212: Formicosepsis biseta (Papp) (Cypselosomatidae), male head; 211: dorsal; 212: anterior. Fig. 213: Formicosepsis sp., male and female copulating, Philippines. Figs 214–215: F. biseta, male: 214: dorsal; 215: lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3670825/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3670827>
    dc:description "FIGURES 216–222. Clisa australis (McAlpine) (Cypselosomatidae), male terminalia; 216: sternites 6–8, ventral; 217: sternite 6 and segment 7 to cerci, lateral; 218: external genitalia, posterior; 219: same, anterior; 220: ejaculatory apodeme; 221: internal genitalia, ventral; 222: same, left lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3670827/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3670829>
    dc:description "FIGURES 223–232. Cypselosoma gephyrae Hendel (Cypselosomatidae), female abdomen; 223: ventral (terminalia retracted); 224: lateral; 225: detail of retracted terminalia; 226: segment 10 and cerci, dorsal; 227: same, lateral; 228: same, ventral; 229: internal genitalia. Figs 230–232: Formicosepsis sp., female abdomen; 230: ventral (terminalia retracted); 231: same, lateral; 232: internal genitalia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3670829/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

